== About

Static is a super simple Rails CMS for Heroku.

Code: http://github.com/trevorturk/static/
Demo: http://static.heroku.com/
Screenshot: http://github.com/trevorturk/static/blob/master/public/screenshot.png


== Requirements 

Rails: http://guides.rubyonrails.org/getting_started.html
Git: http://book.git-scm.com/2_installing_git.html


== Installation

git clone git://github.com/trevorturk/static.git
cd static
sudo gem install bundler
gem bundle
cp config/database.example.yml config/database.yml
cp config/config.example.yml config/config.yml
rake db:create
rake db:schema:load
script/server
# http://localhost:3000/


== Deployment

sudo gem install heroku
heroku create
# Sign up for Amazon S3 at http://aws.amazon.com/s3/ see next step
mate config/config.yml # configure the production environment
rake s3:create
rake heroku:config
git push heroku master
heroku rake db:schema:load
heroku open


== Upgrading

heroku db:pull sqlite://db/backup.sqlite3
git pull
gem bundle
mate config/config.example.yml # review possible changes
rake heroku:config
git push heroku master
heroku rake db:migrate
heroku open


